title: Trouble enlisting in ocean week
body:
I can't enlist for ocean week - I'm logged in and I click on enlist now, "let's do this" comes up yet it never completes. Just stays "enlisting now..."

Anyone else having same issue?

replies.body:
Hey there,

I just enlisted myself with no issue, could you please try on a different browser for me, let me know if this helps.
I was using Safari, gave it a go in Chrome and it worked. Thanks!
